Josephine DUNNIGAN, Administratrix of the Estate of Richard O. Dunnigan, Deceased, v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 1135. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Aug. 27, 1934. Paxton Howard, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. C. E. Bailey, U. S. Atty., of Tulsa, Okl.

Before LEWIS and BRATTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed for failure to prosecute.
